responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "B52BFBB7495881BDC0FCBFB44A392C19", "I\'ve done what you instructed. My men think I am harvesting weapons, and they will never see this coming. Dispensable though they may be, it has cost me some doubt among the dear faithful whom I feed, shelter, and clothe with armor. As I\'m sure you\'re aware, these are gifts easily forgotten among tired soldiers. It is time for you to hold up your end of the deal. I must have your assurance soon.")
name: RVR_ED_M1001_LeoniusPlea_Message_DLG_2_Response
